## ðŸ§  Supported LLM Providers

This library uses [LiteLLM](https://docs.litellm.ai) for LLM integration, supporting 100+ providers:

### Popular Choices

| Provider | Model Example | Vision Support | Cost |
|----------|--------------|----------------|------|
| **OpenAI** | `gpt-4o-mini`, `gpt-4o` | âœ… Yes | ðŸ’° Paid |
| **Google Gemini** | `gemini/gemini-1.5-flash`, `gemini/gemini-1.5-pro` | âœ… Yes | ðŸ’° Paid / Free tier |
| **Anthropic Claude** | `claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022` | âœ… Yes | ðŸ’° Paid |
| **Ollama (Local)** | `ollama_chat/llama3.1`, `ollama_chat/llama3.2-vision` | âœ… Yes | ðŸ†“ Free |

See full provider list: https://docs.litellm.ai/docs/providers

